data.text: Update: Not coughing as much anymore but I still feel sluggish. A bit of flu now and my nose is not as blocked. No more fever hooray. I did another test today and Alhamdulillah it turned out negative but I’m still going to finish my quarantine order and not leave my room 🥴

Sense of taste je is not fully there but bruh i’m always hungry?? Like i hear ppl losing appetite but thats so the opposite. I crave desserts all the time la weh this is not good 🥲 haih anyway i want my energy back haha bcs of this cough, All I wanna do is lie down but i refuse

Today’s update : still coughing a lot, I used to have asthma so this is like not surprising to me so it could take awhile. Breathing is okay la takde sesak. I’ve got my oximeter with me so far its normal. Sumbat hidung is still there, again this is normal to me bcs i have sinus.

Update : Feeling feverish oredi, tgh tunggu oximeter and thermometer sampai jap. And dinner, i ordered marrybrown. Alhamdulillah, selera masih ada ya rakan2. Ini paling penting 😝 later kita duduk depan kdrama and makan
@evavenicaa Thank you eva! You get well soon and have plenty of rest as well! ❤️
@MadihahLatiff latest update is that i dah start rasa nak demam 🥲 hm, thank you so much babe for your prayers 🥺🙆🏻‍♀️
@MadihahLatiff thank you so much babe 🥺 You take care as well kayy 💕
